spec_data.Name: liblouisutdml-doc
spec_data.Description:
liblouisutdml is a braille transcription library for UTDML (Unified Tactile
Document Markup Language) documents. This package contains the user and
developer documentation of the library and the command-line utilities
provided by liblouisutdml-utils.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 27 Feb 2017 08:22:31 AM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Documentation of the library and the corresponding utilities
